reviewText:
We studied this in film school along with spirit of the Beehive.
Both films are about a girl who refuses to be raised  by her family  and instead is raised by
the forces of nature that speak to her head direction, border cells, grid cells, place cells (the Ojos of Don...)
Especially visible in El Nido in the scene where her teacher says "No Me Gusta Dar Consejos de Palabras"
